<mvc:View controllerName="com.zgaur.fiori.workflowuimodule.controller.Main" xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" displayBlock="true" xmlns="sap.m">
    <App id="app">
        <pages>
            <Page id="idPage" showHeader="false" showFooter="false">
                <content>
                    <Panel class="sapUiResponsiveMargin">
                            <headerToolbar>
                                <OverflowToolbar>
                                    <Title text="PO Details"/>
                                </OverflowToolbar>
                            </headerToolbar>
                            <content>
                                <Table id="idProductsTable"
                                       inset="false"
                                       items="{
                                            path: 'context>/filecontent'
                                        }">
                                
                                    <columns>
                                        <Column
                                            width="12em">
                                            <Text text="PO" />
                                        </Column>
                                        <Column
                                            minScreenWidth="Tablet"
                                            demandPopin="true">
                                            <Text text="Action" />
                                        </Column>                                        
                                    </columns>
                                    <items>
                                        <ColumnListItem vAlign="Middle">
                                            <cells>
                                                <Text
                                                    text="{context>PO}" />
                                                <ComboBox selectedKey="{context>ActionPerformed}" editable="{path:'context>ActionPerformed', formatter: '.EditableAction'}">
                                                    <core:Item key="Approved" text="Approve" />
                                                    <core:Item key="Rejected" text="Reject" />
                                                    <core:Item key="na" text="" />
                                                </ComboBox>
                                            </cells>
                                        </ColumnListItem>
                                    </items>
                                </Table>
                            </content>
                        </Panel>
                </content>
            </Page>
        </pages>
    </App>
</mvc:View>
